Purpose of Reports:


    Defect Analysis: Enhances quality control by pinpointing problematic tire types.

    Seasonality Insights: Allows the company to prepare for demand spikes and dips.

    Regional Performance: Optimizes resource allocation by identifying high-performing areas.

    Inventory Efficiency: Reduces carrying costs and minimizes stockouts by analyzing turnover rates.

    Pricing Strategy: Refines pricing decisions by understanding customer price sensitivity.
